4ï¸âƒ£ What does perform_now do?
WelcomeEmailJob.perform_now(user)

Meaning:

Runs immediately

Runs in the same thread

NO Redis

NO Sidekiq

Blocks the request

Equivalent to:

WelcomeEmailJob.new.perform(user)


Use case:

Debugging

Console

Very small tasks

5ï¸âƒ£ What does perform_later do?
WelcomeEmailJob.perform_later(user)

Meaning:

Enqueues job

Sends job to queue adapter (Sidekiq)

Stores job in Redis

Returns immediately

Job runs asynchronously

This is what you use 99% of the time.

