8ï¸âƒ£ Important warning about arguments âš ï¸

Your code:

def perform(user)
end


This works, but is NOT recommended.

Why?

Jobs are serialized

Passing full objects can break

Object may be stale

Best practice:
def perform(user_id)
  user = User.find(user_id)
end


Interviewers LOVE this.

